{"tid":1449674,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"經濟之一 機場 與 貨櫃碼頭","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:00:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:52:18.000Z","uid":30228,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a23a4d239192144ff5d9664a340322dd65cc91d5","tid":1449674,"uid":30228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:00:49.000Z","msg":"據wiki 解說 葵青貨櫃碼頭（英語：Kwai Tsing Container Terminals），早期稱為葵涌貨櫃港（英語：Kwai Chung Container Port）[註 1]、葵涌貨櫃碼頭（英語：Kwai Chung Container Terminals）[註 2]，位於香港新界葵青區藍巴勒海峽兩岸（葵涌－青衣港池），是香港及珠三角的最主要的貨櫃物流處理中心，對華南極為重要，目前是全球第八大貨櫃港<br />\n<br />\n 每逢颱風吹襲香港，並且帶來強風或嚴重交通事故，葵青貨櫃碼頭便會逐步停止運作。當風暴過後，前往交收貨物的貨櫃車往往會將附近道路擠至水洩不通，導致公共運輸癱瘓做成延誤"},{"pid":"1c1fb93e3348f2656ccefb742556c6da5c1ca52b","tid":1449674,"uid":30228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:02:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"70467af024a2d50ddb8fa2aa91ec33c031de33b2","tid":1449674,"uid":30228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7c5bfc330024e4c7df766742c393e57f46bd7286","tid":1449674,"uid":30228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:05:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"abd8ad399470c50cdc56bebe84469e6e44d23a21","tid":1449674,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:05:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"037ae6f9b69340fbb7094465f47673034fd4be4e","tid":1449674,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:05:55.000Z","msg":"召喚文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb845af9a9ac088201ae3f0395cff8cf8f9f838","tid":1449674,"uid":30228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:06:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"196678563a5d7d3518192e3a6063295a71769e42","tid":1449674,"uid":30228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:09:54.000Z","msg":"push,